The swing class is used in java to build gui application.
The Basic.java class defines a very basic gui application using JFRAME container,components and a swingclass to display the app.
The MainFrame class is well defined class that extends the JFRAME.class,its function is to act as a controller organinsing all the component that will be displayed.
    In the example above these componenets come from the Toolbar and the textpanel class.
The TextPanel and the toolbox is defined so that each component and its activities can be defined seperately,then added to the Mainframe,these helps for easy debugging.